dcterms:description: PTBXL encompasses 21,837 ECG signals collected from 18,885 patients, consisting of 12-lead ECG, each sampled at a rate of 500 Hz for 10 seconds, with multi-label classification tasks across four subsets.
dcterms:title: PTBXL

dcterms:description: The Chapman-Shaoxing-Ningbo (CSN) dataset is a large-scale 12-lead electrocardiogram database for arrhythmia study, comprising 45,152 standard ECG records.
